{"tid":404461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"痔瘡，肛裂求救","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T11:34:58.000Z","uid":127314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83be682255f54cada312b5e4db2fb824458bf260","tid":404461,"uid":127314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"痔瘡有左好多年，間中熱氣會屙血，都習慣左<br />\n但近年開始有肛裂...如果有呢個病你就知道，佢係肛門/腸道既病入面痛楚最大，最痛苦既病<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好番2個月，又會爆一次。。無限loop，已有年半<br />\n已經有用溫水坐浴， 硝酸甘油脂（放鬆括約肌），乳果糖（軟化大便）<br />\n<br />\n應該要做手術，有冇人都有做過呢個手術，or冇呢個病可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba5e1982ccdd32731eefcebda3506275ace511f","tid":404461,"uid":127314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:24:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43189e61234cce56295ed0120475fa576ef54c13","tid":404461,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"要拮屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92d5182b01becf56bb607a71c808d03d78bdeb3","tid":404461,"uid":44031,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:26:50.000Z","msg":"剛烈係咪要抽卡判定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f541f7cfcf336fe619ef786fb03056b8f1eded","tid":404461,"uid":127314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要拮屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果要做手術就一定啦..."},{"pid":"d9357c466b3cc3d101f733e2220fc8ce8a7ea525","tid":404461,"uid":127314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剛烈係咪要抽卡判定？<img src=\"/as