得返。</blockquote><br />\n塞keyboard會唔會快d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492d5e286f8d78ebf1b38bdb7c063d9c554027a6","tid":404461,"uid":127314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92391034e461dfc46c1a400389622a0bdf212eb9","tid":404461,"uid":44031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.e3ol.com/news/upfiles/2011/201111314153337074.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e3ol.com%2Fnews%2Fupfiles%2F2011%2F201111314153337074.jpg&h=96ac0507&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係我講果個"},{"pid":"2a454a6bb322300960a3034f82fa8308b98fcc26","tid":404461,"uid":120202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我痛左兩個幾禮拜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇左醫生都係開左兩日止痛藥同埋塞肛門個d痔瘡藥<br />\n兩日之後雖然冇咁痛但都係keep住痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日都生不如死<br />\n屙屎痛 屙尿痛 坐底痛 總之一縮肛就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0fce887a747acb856614c0d027d44447616dec","tid":404461,"uid":127314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我痛左兩個幾禮拜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇左醫生都係開左兩日止痛藥同埋塞肛門個d痔瘡藥<br />\n兩日之後雖然冇咁痛但都係keep住痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日都生不如死<br />\n屙屎痛 屙尿痛 坐底痛 總之一縮肛就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係肛裂定痔瘡？<br />\n如果係肛裂，要用硝酸甘油脂，係肛裂既特效藥<br />\n但得浸會，法國醫院有"},{"pid":"397cf4f3f073b3319e81b389935d7a0b47996887","tid":404461,"uid":120202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我痛左兩個幾禮拜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇左醫生都係開左兩日止痛藥同埋塞肛門個d痔瘡藥<br />\n兩日之後雖然冇咁痛但都係keep住痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日都生不如死<br />\n屙屎痛 屙尿痛 坐底痛 總之一縮肛就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係肛裂定痔瘡？<br />\n如果係肛裂，要用硝酸甘油脂，係肛裂既特效藥<br />\n但得浸會，法國醫院有</blockquote><br />\n我淨係睇過樓下家庭醫生 佢就咁睇我菊花話我肛裂 話會自己好翻 但我已經痛左就黎一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家菊花出面仲多左粒好似暗瘡既野 一郁佢就痛 都唔知睇咩醫生好"}]}